
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-thurlow-nfsv4-namespace-01.txt'>
    <title>"A Namespace For NFS Version 4", Robert Thurlow</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-thurlow-nfsv4-namespace-01.txt</link>
    <description>Recent work on Replication and Migration for NFSv4 has reminded us of a more fundamental problem: NFS currently lacks a coherent enterprise or global namespace. With changes in a minor revision of NFS Version 4, this can be addressed to make services like replication and migration of filesystems fully functional.</description>
    <dc:date>2005-02-21T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
